N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 933.5 - Multiple Non-Gifts

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall be construed as relieving a
covered person's obligations under Public Officers Law section 74 with respect
to the solicitation, receipt, or acceptance of multiple items, services, or any
other things of value that, individually, are not gifts solely because each has
less than nominal value. Notes
